OL,3,CMan dies after being found critically
OL,4,Cinjured overnight
OL,6,FA man's death is being treated as
OL,7,Fsuspicious after he was found
OL,8,Fcritically injured inside a property
OL,9,Fin South Gloucestershire.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called
OL,12,Fovernight to a sudden death at an
OL,13,Faddress in Cleve Road, Filton, and
OL,14,FAvon and Somerset Police has confirmed
OL,15,Fthat the man could not be saved.
OL,17,FA cordon and road closures remain in
OL,18,Fplace in Filton while investigations
OL,19,Fcontinue.
