OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1775830265
OL,3,CMan dies after being found critically
OL,4,Cinjured overnight
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said: "His
OL,7,Fnext of kin has been informed, and we
OL,8,Foffer our condolences to his family at
OL,9,Fthis extremely difficult time."
OL,11,FThe force also urged the public "not
OL,12,Fto speculate around the circumstances"
OL,13,Fof his death.
